<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 13 Oct 2024 18:17:49 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>萨巴伦卡战胜郑和自己夺得武汉冠军</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/sabalenka-overcomes-zheng-herself-win-wuhan-title-2024-10-13/</link><description>世界排名第二的选手萨巴伦卡周日表示，在武汉公开赛决赛中，萨巴伦卡以 6-3、5-7、6-3 的比分战胜了本土热门郑钦文，她失去了注意力，有时成为了自己最大的敌人。</description><pubDate>Sun, 13 Oct 2024 14:27:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/sabalenka-overcomes-zheng-herself-win-wuhan-title-2024-10-13/</guid></item><item><title>辛纳平息场外骚乱夺得上海大师赛冠军</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/sinner-blocks-out-off-court-turmoil-win-shanghai-masters-2024-10-13/</link><description>世界排名第一的辛纳表示，在周日以 7-6(4) 6-3 击败诺瓦克·德约科维奇夺得上海大师赛桂冠后，他尽最大努力从容应对，避免持续的兴奋剂争议影响他的表现。</description><pubDate>Sun, 13 Oct 2024 14:14:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/sinner-blocks-out-off-court-turmoil-win-shanghai-masters-2024-10-13/</guid></item><item><title>萨巴伦卡击败本土热门郑智后连续第三次夺得武汉公开赛冠军</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/sabalenka-wins-third-straight-wuhan-open-title-after-beating-home-favourite-2024-10-13/</link><description>萨巴伦卡在首盘比赛中轰出7个ace球和32个制胜分，并且没有面临任何一个破发点。</description><pubDate>Sun, 13 Oct 2024 12:42:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/sabalenka-wins-third-straight-wuhan-open-title-after-beating-home-favourite-2024-10-13/</guid></item><item><title>中国总理可能在访问巴基斯坦期间为北京资助的机场揭幕</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-premier-could-inaugurate-beijing-funded-airport-pakistan-during-visit-2024-10-13/</link><description>信息部长阿陶拉·塔拉尔周日告诉记者，中国总理李强可能会在下周访问巴基斯坦期间为巴基斯坦俾路支省的一个中资机场启用运营。</description><pubDate>Sun, 13 Oct 2024 11:20:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-premier-could-inaugurate-beijing-funded-airport-pakistan-during-visit-2024-10-13/</guid></item><item><title>辛纳夺得上海大师赛冠军 德约科维奇等待第100个冠军头衔</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/sinner-wins-shanghai-masters-extend-djokovics-wait-100th-title-2024-10-13/</link><description>詹尼克·辛纳 (Jannik Sinner) 成为上海有史以来最年轻的冠军。</description><pubDate>Sun, 13 Oct 2024 10:52:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/sinner-wins-shanghai-masters-extend-djokovics-wait-100th-title-2024-10-13/</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦分裂主义武装分子 BLA 否认参与了地雷袭击</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pakistan-separatist-militants-bla-deny-involvement-attack-mines-2024-10-13/</link><description>巴基斯坦激进分离主义组织俾路支解放军否认参与了导致至少 21 名矿工死亡的袭击事件，并谴责暴力事件。</description><pubDate>Sun, 13 Oct 2024 07:58:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pakistan-separatist-militants-bla-deny-involvement-attack-mines-2024-10-13/</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚致力于继续复兴，波波维奇面临熟悉的敌人</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/popovic-faces-familiar-foe-australia-aim-continue-renaissance-japan-2024-10-13/</link><description>波波维奇接替格雷厄姆·阿诺德后的首场比赛带领澳大利亚队以3-1战胜中国队，重燃了自动晋级2026年世界杯的希望。</description><pubDate>Sun, 13 Oct 2024 07:56:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/popovic-faces-familiar-foe-australia-aim-continue-renaissance-japan-2024-10-13/</guid></item><item><title>东盟敦促尽早就南海规则达成一致，结束缅甸暴力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/asean-urges-early-accord-south-china-sea-code-end-myanmar-violence-2024-10-13/</link><description>东南亚领导人周日呼吁迅速就基于国际法的南海行为准则达成一致，同时要求缅甸立即停止战斗并进行包容性和平谈判以结束内战。</description><pubDate>Sun, 13 Oct 2024 07:28:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/asean-urges-early-accord-south-china-sea-code-end-myanmar-violence-2024-10-13/</guid></item><item><title>台湾发现中国航母，中国军事视频称“已做好战斗准备”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-spots-chinese-carrier-china-military-video-says-prepared-battle-2024-10-13/</link><description>中国不排除使用武力将台湾置于其控制之下。</description><pubDate>Sun, 13 Oct 2024 07:24:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-spots-chinese-carrier-china-military-video-says-prepared-battle-2024-10-13/</guid></item><item><title>岑浩辉当选澳门候任行政长官</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/sam-hou-fai-elected-chief-executive-designate-macau-2024-10-13/</link><description>政府周日表示，前法官岑浩辉当选中国澳门候任行政长官，使他成为毗邻香港、以赌场为主的地区的领导人。</description><pubDate>Sun, 13 Oct 2024 05:11:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/sam-hou-fai-elected-chief-executive-designate-macau-2024-10-13/</guid></item><item><title>越南与中国领导人会晤签署农产品贸易、支付等10项协议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnam-china-sign-10-documents-during-chinese-premiers-visit-hanoi-2024-10-13/</link><description>在中国总理李强对河内进行为期三天的访问期间，越南和中国周日签署了从农业合作到跨境二维码支付等十项协议，这两个邻国寻求加强关系。</description><pubDate>Sun, 13 Oct 2024 04:29:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnam-china-sign-10-documents-during-chinese-premiers-visit-hanoi-2024-10-13/</guid></item><item><title>9月份中国通货紧缩压力加大消费者通胀降温</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-consumer-inflation-cools-sept-ppi-deflation-deepens-2024-10-13/</link><description>中国9月份消费者通胀意外放缓，而生产者价格通缩加剧，加大了北京方面迅速推出更多刺激措施以重振疲弱需求和不稳定经济活动的压力。</description><pubDate>Sun, 13 Oct 2024 01:48:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-consumer-inflation-cools-sept-ppi-deflation-deepens-2024-10-13/</guid></item><item><title>美国官员指责俄罗斯和中国阻止亚洲领导人发表声明</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-official-accuses-russia-china-blocking-asia-leaders-statement-2024-10-12/</link><description>一位美国官员表示，他们的反对主要是针对有争议的南海问题上的措辞。</description><pubDate>Sat, 12 Oct 2024 22:50:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-official-accuses-russia-china-blocking-asia-leaders-statement-2024-10-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国总理在河内同意加强与越南的关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-premier-hanoi-agrees-boost-ties-with-vietnam-2024-10-12/</link><description>越南政府表示，越南和中国周六同意加强防务和安全合作，尽管两国在南海存在多年的海上争端。</description><pubDate>Sat, 12 Oct 2024 17:29:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-premier-hanoi-agrees-boost-ties-with-vietnam-2024-10-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国警告欧盟不要单独进行电动汽车价格谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-urges-eu-not-affect-ev-tariff-talks-with-separate-price-negotiations-2024-10-12/</link><description>中国周六敦促欧盟不要就中国制造的电动汽车在欧盟销售的价格进行单独谈判，警告称这将“动摇双边关税谈判的基础”。</description><pubDate>Sat, 12 Oct 2024 10:02:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-urges-eu-not-affect-ev-tariff-talks-with-separate-price-negotiations-2024-10-12/</guid></item></channel></rss>